text: The following lists events that happened during 2012 in Cape Verde. ==Incumbents== *President: Jorge Carlos Fonseca *Prime Minister: José Maria Neves ==Events== *A campus of the Universidade de Santiago opened in the São José Seminary in Praia *March 8: São Vicente's airport name became Cesária Évora Airport *July 1: 2012 local elections took place ==Sports== *Sporting Clube da Praia won the Cape Verdean Football Championship ==References== Category:Years of the 21st century in Cape Verde Category:2010s in Cape Verde Cape Verde Cape Verde
title: 2012 in Cape Verde
